<p>We prefer payment by online bank transfer as it is the quickest, simplest option until we 
set up our own online payment gateway. We also accept payment by cheque or DD.</p>

<ul class="payment">
  <li>
    <%= f.radio_button(:payment_method, "1") %>
    <p><strong>Online bank transfer</strong></p>
    <p>Bank account details follow. Please email us the confirmation once you
    transfer funds. Do contact us if you need help, or more information.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= f.radio_button(:payment_method, "2") %>
    <p><strong>Cheque</strong></p>
    <p>Please post the cheque to the address that follows, with your name
    clearly written at the back.</p>
  </li>
</ul>